text: Beni M'Tir is a Tunisian commune in the Jendouba Governorate. It lies at an altitude of 650 metres and has a population of 811.« La villégiature sereine au concret », Le Renouveau, 2 février 2008, p. 7 ==References== Category:Populated places in Jendouba Governorate Category:Communes of Tunisia
title: Beni M'Tir
